QuestData.Title: Home Again
QuestData.Description: Ya should find Keely. She'll be eager for word.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Keely Dunwald at the Dunwald Holdout.
QuestData.RewardText: Thank you for bandin' my brothers back together. I know they're tough, but they're even tougher when they're side by side, and there's a lot of Twilight out there.$B$BYou're good to put a gal's heart at ease.
